  "task_html": "\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#706b62;margin-bottom:16px;\">⏱ Versuche die Aufgaben ohne Taschenrechner zu lösen. Fülle alle Felder aus und überprüfe dann deine Antworten.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rep-grid\">\n\n  <div class=\"rep-item\">\n    <div class=\"rep-num\">1</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-q\">Welche Zahlen haben den Betrag 3? <span class=\"rep-hint\">(|3| = 3)</span></div>\n    <div class=\"rep-inputs\">\n      <input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"rep-text\" data-check=\"3;-3\" placeholder=\"Antwort …\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"rep-item\">\n    <div class=\"rep-num\">2</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-q\">0,1³ =</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-inputs\">\n      <input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.001\" placeholder=\"?\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"rep-item\">\n    <div class=\"rep-num\">3</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-q\">Schreibe als Dezimalbruch in h: 18 min</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-inputs\">\n      <input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.3\" placeholder=\"? h\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"rep-item\">\n    <div class=\"rep-num\">4</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-q\">Erkläre den Begriff <em>Spannweite</em> einer Stichprobe.</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-inputs\">\n      <textarea class=\"cell-textarea\" data-ans=\"rep-open\" placeholder=\"Deine Erklärung …\" rows=\"2\"></textarea>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"rep-item\">\n    <div class=\"rep-num\">5</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-q\">Klammere aus: 24xy − 16xz + 8x =</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-inputs\">\n      <input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"rep-text\" data-check=\"8x(3y-2z+1);8x(3y − 2z + 1)\" placeholder=\"Ergebnis …\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"rep-item\">\n    <div class=\"rep-num\">6</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-q\">Gib in kg an: 27 g</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-inputs\">\n      <input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.027\" placeholder=\"? kg\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"rep-item\">\n    <div class=\"rep-num\">7</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-q\">A<sub>Trapez</sub> = _____ ?</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-inputs\">\n      <input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"rep-text\" data-check=\"(a+c)/2*h;(a+c)·h/2\" placeholder=\"Formel …\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"rep-item\">\n    <div class=\"rep-num\">8</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-q\">Gib die allgemeine Formel einer linearen Funktion an.</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-inputs\">\n      <input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"rep-text\" data-check=\"y=mx+b;f(x)=mx+b;mx+b\" placeholder=\"Formel …\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"rep-item\">\n    <div class=\"rep-num\">9</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-q\">½ + ⅓ =</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-inputs\">\n      <input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"rep-text\" data-check=\"5/6;0.8333\" placeholder=\"?\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"rep-item\">\n    <div class=\"rep-num\">10</div>\n    <div class=\"rep-q\">Berechne 40 % von 15 €. <span class=\"rep-hint\">(ohne TR!)</span></div>\n    <div class=\"rep-inputs\">\n      <input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"6\" placeholder=\"? €\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"check-bar\">\n  <button class=\"btn-check\" onclick=\"checkRep()\">✓ Überprüfen</button>\n  <button class=\"btn-reset\" onclick=\"resetRep()\">↺ Zurücksetzen</button>\n  <span class=\"check-result\" id=\"check-result-rep\"></span>\n</div>\n",
  "sol_html": "\n<div class=\"rep-grid\">\n  <div class=\"rep-item\"><div class=\"rep-num\">1</div><div class=\"rep-q\"><strong>−3 und 3</strong></div></div>\n  <div class=\"rep-item\"><div class=\"rep-num\">2</div><div class=\"rep-q\"><strong>0,001</strong></div></div>\n  <div class=\"rep-item\"><div class=\"rep-num\">3</div><div class=\"rep-q\"><strong>0,3 h</strong></div></div>\n  <div class=\"rep-item\"><div class=\"rep-num\">4</div><div class=\"rep-q\"><strong>Die Differenz zwischen dem größten und dem kleinsten Wert einer Stichprobe.</strong></div></div>\n  <div class=\"rep-item\"><div class=\"rep-num\">5</div><div class=\"rep-q\"><strong>8x(3y − 2z + 1)</strong></div></div>\n  <div class=\"rep-item\"><div class=\"rep-num\">6</div><div class=\"rep-q\"><strong>0,027 kg</strong></div></div>\n  <div class=\"rep-item\"><div class=\"rep-num\">7</div><div class=\"rep-q\"><strong>A<sub>Trapez</sub> = (a + c) / 2 · h</strong></div></div>\n  <div class=\"rep-item\"><div class=\"rep-num\">8</div><div class=\"rep-q\"><strong>y = mx + b</strong></div></div>\n  <div class=\"rep-item\"><div class=\"rep-num\">9</div><div class=\"rep-q\"><strong>5/6</strong></div></div>\n  <div class=\"rep-item\"><div class=\"rep-num\">10</div><div class=\"rep-q\"><strong>6 €</strong></div></div>\n</div>\n"
